{"tid":1722333,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"關於被自殺，大家有無發現有共通點","createTime":"2019-11-15T01:02:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T10:46:19.000Z","uid":263103,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"b991585f2dd30e97a01f6d49c76ddd787e723d36","tid":1722333,"uid":263103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:02:40.000Z","msg":"1. 哨兵<br />\n2. 非前線<br />\n3. 行徑貌似被指示約到某處<br />\n4. cctv遲遲未有 正常一開就有 <br />\n<br />\n跟據有人提供既資料，過去數月都會有人被起底恐嚇，同時有啲人既家人朋友上司同事資料都被列出，用作恐嚇要佢地收皮，聲稱會對佢地識既人不利，仲講明報警都無用。<br />\n<br />\n依個人猜測，過去既死者當中，極大機會有人操控被要求去某啲地點。<br />\n<br />\n大家請幫手教育一下身邊朋友，唔好怕哩啲恐嚇!!<br />\n<br />\n如果收到有人恐嚇要你地點做，要求唔可講比人知 ，否則殺你家人等，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">請第一時間搵議員同律師!!</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n報警係無用，因為好多資料係由警署個database流出，有人故意比出去定中共有得access我唔知。但可肯定佢地有既資料一定係警署資料為主。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但大家唔好絕望灰心，我地仲有好多方法。<br />\n而且為左保護身邊愛既人，只有自己確保自己安全下先可以真正咁保護到<br />\n<br />\n公開所有恐嚇資料先更會得到街坊幫忙同保護。<br />\n所以唔好怕，我地香港人每個都齊上齊落! 對抗哩個惡魔政權!! 重新修正成個香港與政務。<br />\n<br />\n因為你地死左，你地家人為你查真相其實都一樣會無命，所以唔好咁傻聽人指示去被自殺!!<br />\n<br />\n記住所有人每日都要向至少2個朋友定時錄音報到，同<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">定立暗號</span></span>。大家聽到留音就知發生事去幫你。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n尤其哨兵行動唔好咁明顯，觀察有無可疑人士先，開live location比信得過既後勤，停左或被終止就知咩事。最好兩三個朋友一齊。<br />\n<br />\n請相信香港人，我地並不孤單! <br />\n我地要比佢地長命! 我地仲要重建香港，仲要睇住啲仆街點落台，開香賓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n萬事大吉。<br />\n<br />\n願榮光歸香港!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b87983f54d159995603fb6fa235dedb585fd8110","tid":1722333,"uid":263103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T01:31:21.000Z","msg":"p左n個月 推唔撚到po <br />\n有無手足幫幫手 救人意識po好重要"},{"pid":"26d31ed70d05bd0075e4e1146057d2746e653e97","tid":1722333,"uid":263103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:16:21.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"876b8546eaf51c01926b7e693309e128e3191cdf","tid":1722333,"uid":190002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:30:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"87a2b7f305e47f41b7d42e1f0be312f9ba614dde","tid":1722333,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:31:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8cd303b6eec7850e49cb5395c6c9086401e0c6c","tid":1722333,"uid":328812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:31:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a1d85230530e70b444c3ed37c6c7da33f06d4a73","tid":1722333,"uid":328812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:32:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"66aad6a6250a9cfd3bff9c6538d76a5d4971cda0","tid":1722333,"uid":144084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:32:40.000Z","msg":"【黑警陷入恐慌!】微博瘋傳13休班警被伏擊<br />\n對家士氣<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong> -40</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n都係踢春袋，最本少利大，我地需要極大量呢類型行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1722529/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1722529/</a>"},{"pid":"287667db93890ad0c82b4e5d6716938ee7cacd59","tid":1722333,"uid":37641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:44:40.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"d64823be1840f68241309c1531ae9f11c38d5f93","tid":1722333,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:46:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推，<br />\n<br />\n仲有， 估計<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連登</span></span>亦都被<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">滲透</span></span>得好勁<br />\n